Code
avgAlbedo = (iceExtent / 100 * 0.6) + ((100 - iceExtent) / 100 * 0.06)
absorbedEnergy = ((1 - avgAlbedo) * 100).toFixed(1)
reflectedEnergy = (avgAlbedo * 100).toFixed(1)

html`
